The finalised database is included in this repo, however if you're interested the scripts are attached.

To use these scripts to reproduce the database. Download recipe NLG from here: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/saldenisov/recipenlg?resource=download
Donwload what's cooking from here https://www.kaggle.com/c/whats-cooking/data

You can use requirments.txt to build a python venv, or just install ntlk using pip.




